data.title: Funeral Notices
data.meta_description: Find local and national death notices, funeral notices, obituaries, in memoriams, acknowledgements and family announcements including birthdays, births, anniversaries and marriages at funeral-notices.co.uk
data.text:
KenGATWARDGATWARD - KEN, January 13, 2014. A true gentleman, passed peacefully following an illness bravely borne. Husband to Evelyn (deceased). Beloved dad to Sandy, Julie and Hazel and loved father in law to Rob, Richard and Rick, cherished gramps to Sarah, Katy, Michael, Emily, Christopher and Joanne. All enquiries to Thompsons F.S., 175a Liverpool Road South, Maghull, L31 8AA. Tel: 0151 526 1815.

Keep me informed of updates
